data.title: Clark Haggans, Former Steelers Linebacker Dies Aged 46
data.meta_description: Former Steelers linebacker Clark Haggans, a member of the Super Bowl XL-winning team in 2005, has passed away at the age of 46.
data.text: Former Steelers linebacker Clark Haggans, a member of the Super Bowl XL-winning team in 2005, has passed away at the age of 46.
